# A sample project with the express( project with the MVC folder strcture ) and Mocah, Chai for test cases.

----
### Dependencies
Express 4.0 (A minimilistic NodeJs framework)

----
MongoDb 3.2.4 (A non-relational data to store document object)

----
Mongoose 3.1.4 (MongoDb ODM)

----
Jsonwebtoken 7.2.1 (For Api token authentication)

----
Node-mail 2.7.0 (For smtp mail transport)

----
### Dev dependencies
Chai 3.5.0 (A asseration library)

----
Chai-http 2.0.1 (A http resquest library for test case)

----
Mocha 2.4.5 (A testing framework for NodeJs application)



